               stealing, on the <rs id="t18320906-210-cd1183" type="crimeDate">28th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320906-210-off1182 t18320906-210-cd1183"></join>, 1 watch-case, value 10s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18320906-210-victim1747" type="victimName">
